caption:
“I just promised myself that I would keep going and I wouldn't sit still.” 

Meet Thomas Panek 🏃 husband, father, CEO of @LighthouseGuild and marathon runner. Stay tuned for Thomas’ #HumansOfHOKA film to learn how he turned challenge into purpose and how he continues to inspire others to keep going. 💪 Full film premiering Wednesday 4/30 on YouTube.
